<a href="<%= @card_url %>"><%= @card.name %></a> was <%= @action %> by <%= @updater %> at <%= @card.updated_at %>.
<%- if @action=='edited' -%>
You can also see <a href="<%= @change_url %>">what changed</a>.
<%- end %>                                                     
<%- if @subedits.present? -%>
This update included the following changes:
	<%- @subedits.each do |name, action| -%>
  <%= action %> <%= name %>
	<%- end -%>
<%- end -%>